               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Takla Hāymānot “Vita of Takla Haymanot” (fols. 3ra-123rb)&#xD;
II) Maṣḥafa lǝdätu la-ʾabuna Takla Hāymānot “Book of the Genealogy of ʾabuna Takla Haymanot” (fols. 123va-126rb)&#xD;
- Genealogy of Takla Hāymānot (fols. 123va-124vb)&#xD;
- Wa-nabara ʾabbā Yoḥanni ba-Dabra Dāmmo... “And ʾabbā Yoḥanni lived in Dabra Dāmmo...” (fols. 124vb-125rb)&#xD;
- Zenā mänakosat “The Story of the Monks” (fols. 125rb-126rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-4; colophon.</summary>
